### [Protected] Get current system settings
GET {{host}}/api/settings
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

### [Protected] Update system settings (Simulating Admin changing threshold)
PUT {{host}}/api/settings
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

{
  "globalThreshold": 0.095,
  "detectionEnabled": true,
  "logRetentionDays": 30
}

### ---------------- NEGATIVE TESTS ---------------- ###

### [Negative] Update settings with invalid data (Expected: 400 Bad Request)
PUT {{host}}/api/settings
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

{
  "globalThreshold": -5.0,
  "detectionEnabled": true,
  "logRetentionDays": -10
}

### [Negative] Get settings without token (Expected: 401 Unauthorized)
GET {{host}}/api/settings